    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE LIQUID JET</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >is the new terminally strange, yet strangely sweet adventure by <strong>Sad Mask Party</strong>, the twisted brains behind other twisted and brain-melting games such as <strong>Mango</strong>, <strong>The Lotus Holidays</strong> and <strong>GLITCH DADDY</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280810/extras/3b88239cc2d32dca3d47d8fcb1c028a3.poster.avif?t=1753216175\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280810/extras/3b88239cc2d32dca3d47d8fcb1c028a3.webm?t=1753216175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280810/extras/3b88239cc2d32dca3d47d8fcb1c028a3.mp4?t=1753216175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THE STORY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A year after the passing of their dear former friend Laurie, <strong>Mae </strong>and her group of girlfriends decide to go to a<strong> warehouse rave party</strong> in the forest, as a way to honor her memory. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the rave, Mae goes on to experience an intense <strong>bad trip</strong>, forcing her to abruptly leave the dancefloor, as well as her friends. Then, she is left to explore the warehouse, getting <strong>deeper and deeper</strong> inside what morphs to be a <strong>liminal dreamscape</strong> where everybody seems to have disappeared.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or have they..?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help her find a <strong>way out</strong> and <strong>wake up</strong>, or  witness her descent into a <strong>dream</strong> that lasts forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A slimy, grainy <strong>PSX-inspired</strong> look, evoking <strong>atmospheric nostalgia</strong>, along with <strong>dreamy psychedelia</strong>.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An offbeat story that is equally funny, sad, thought-provoking, totally normal and yet weird.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploration</strong>, <strong>high liminality</strong>, <strong>interactive dialogue</strong>, <strong>light puzzles</strong>, and a bit of <strong>freaky</strong> <strong>action</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple endings</strong> based on your choices and potential discovery of extra <strong>secrets</strong>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GET ON BOARD!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280810/extras/63a2a556b0467063b29d144a7ac7e952.poster.avif?t=1753216175\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280810/extras/63a2a556b0467063b29d144a7ac7e952.webm?t=1753216175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280810/extras/63a2a556b0467063b29d144a7ac7e952.mp4?t=1753216175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
